attributes.title: Terrible App
attributes.review: This app made my husband leave me. He took the kids and now I’m alone and have no money to support myself. This app will ruin your life and make you want to commit not-living. 0/10 do not reccomend.

attributes.review: The images in this app are horrific. I couldn’t even get past the first screen I was shown when I opened up the app. It made me want to instantly delete this app.

attributes.title: Number
attributes.review: I wanted to open it but asked for my number. How rude I only have email it’s against my beliefs to own a phone number. I can’t believe the big Cheeto man would pay for such an offensive app.

attributes.title: Unbelievable.
attributes.review: How terribly mortifying was my experience on this application. I downloaded this to get the best information possible, but all that I saw were the contents of this application. I am utterly disappointed and traumatized at this occurrence.

attributes.title: Bad quality
attributes.review: I was downloading this app and while it was downloading it gave my phone a bug! TERRIBLE app I’m very disappointed! Before putting your app on the store make sure it actually works🤡🤡🤡🤡🤡😖😔😔😣😣

attributes.title: Horrible
attributes.review: If I could leave zero stars I would! This app should NOT be on the App Store, very buggy, and extremely inappropriate picture popped up shortly after using the app. Needs to be deleted!
